					<![CDATA[
						 <p>(1) Ehhh. I don't really care for this Little Mister. I sorta like the log (though it's borderline forced), but this take on the concept of a Mr. Soap is boring.</p> <p>(2) Multi-canon and all, but I preferred the version of Little Misters lists that weren't necessarily consistent, and that didn't always have you becoming Mr. Collector. It's not that a different version of that is bad (I actually like that Mr. Soap is on both), just that this New List is less interesting and pretty derivative. I mean, really, this list has a Mr. Redd equivalent on it too? (The only real divergence is not even one &quot;Ms.&quot; - bleh.)</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
